{"tid":2028011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最後的香港精神—港禱文","createTime":"2020-05-21T15:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T02:45:23.000Z","uid":65213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"84ff6f5c13352389169e37f5592652bce5b2bd84","tid":2028011,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我們在光復之地，願人都以香港的名為榮，<br />\n願光復的路來臨，<br />\n用我們的意志對抗暴政，如同行兒女一樣，<br />\n我們抗爭的精神，早已留在心中，<br />\n免我們的血，如前路人免我們的淚，<br />\n不叫我們互相分化，但求我們改變歷史<br />\n因為榮光，煲底，自由全屬於你<br />\n直到永遠<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"65413f04673bf16efc4ed6d0b61224216ec405c8","tid":2028011,"uid":67339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"118090214c8563c2a02708d1f505d55a39e0300a","tid":2028011,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:19:06.000Z","msg":"香港人出來呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4866e0420b1322d0932ff4acf384f3ee2fa87139","tid":2028011,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffdbf3fb409e93e4701c50cf71e9d27aa34af8a6","tid":2028011,"uid":324405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b77e3d2ca756a3bf6978c6822a6c8e2d342b70","tid":2028011,"uid":256508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}